dc_description_s: This data layer represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Bayfield County in 2020. [The purpose of this layer is to organize section corner points with GPS coordinate information for the Public Land Survey System (PLSS). This feature class is the final layer made from other combined feature class datasets.Link to metadata information: https://www.bayfieldcounty.org/437/GIS-Metadata]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: [https://www.bayfieldcounty.org/892/GIS-Data-Download]
